data.title: Hunt on for Indonesian spy
data.meta_description: Australian intelligence authorities are investigating information that a senior Canberra official is working as an Indonesian agent.
data.text:
Australian intelligence authorities are investigating information that a senior Canberra official is working as an Indonesian agent.

According to the highly sensitive information, the official has been recruited by an Indonesian intelligence agency called Badan Intelijen Strategis (BAIS).
